To facilitate deployment of the FieldTrip buffer with BCI2000, a stable 
and well-tested version of the buffer source code is included with BCI2000. 
This version corresponds to buffer-20080712.zip

The official releases of the FieldTrip buffer software can be found at
  http://www.ru.nl/fcdonders/fieldtrip
and
  ftp://ftp.fcdonders.nl/pub/fieldtrip/modules

